  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just trying to get home. It’s only a quarter mile. One street. What could go wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why does everything seem so dangerous?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why are you the only one here?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And most importantly, why can’t you just go around?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-60 minutes (or longer, depending on level of patience).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking Simulator.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No save points.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >May contain jumpscares </p></li></ul>",
